/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真fans表示好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:35:21.000Z","msg":"我就唔信你未試過J佢"},{"pid":"831974e9064bb52d8ef2016a2275464ea37d365d","tid":816413,"uid":108329,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T21:59:19.000Z","msg":"陰陽頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099ef593e74704a5227376a10df466252282e7a2","tid":816413,"uid":202767,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5bc8a641d3bee7629027945b02311ac8eebc3440","tid":816413,"uid":22861,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:30:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好用Avril<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真fans表示好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"佢啲碟我夠買齊啦，唔通我唔係真fans？<br />\n？ 但佢真係好好j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e4d61e81edf66d6c9e78944aa16c58e0d05294","tid":816413,"uid":202767,"like":0,"dislike":44,"score":-44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T03:55:54.000Z","msg":"小弟英文唔好， 如果錯grammar希望大家唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n我係阿ray毒l一名， 平時返學放學自己一個，食飯呢入廁所,唔好話破處，同人傾計都難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢日我如是放學去starbucks打工做收鋃，我發呆之際突然聽見一把甜美既聲音{can i have a grande latte please?}<br />\n呢個女仔笑容甜美，有著一把令人陶醉的金髮，目測15x非常可愛，身穿白色小羊裝，到了此時，巨龍不自覺的抬起了頭。我發呆凝望之際，又有一把聲音驚醒了我，{hey!can you hear me???} 我整個人彈了起來連忙道歉說{sorry miss~ what's your name?}她說{Melissa}.{ok,plz wait for moment}我說。{ok,here's your latte,enjoy~}之後她頭也不回的離開了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放工時已是深夜，天上下起大雨來，一名濕透了身的嬌小女子站在店外的帳篷前，這不是今天那個金髮女孩嗎?怎會站在那裏？我走過去禮貌的問{are you Miss Melissa?what are you doing here?}她說{oh !you're the coffee guy today , i forgot to bring the umbrella,i have to wait my maneger pick me up} 我囗震震的説{my name is Ray,if you don'mine,my home is near by here,you can go there to tidy up yourself}我以為她會毫不猶豫的拒絕我，誰知她竟然爽快的答應了，就這樣，我們一同在傘下，第一次緩步回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6545f45df9595198c122f33a911b2f100c57d569","tid":816413,"uid":202767,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:00:46.000Z","msg":"希望大家鐘意，多廿個正皮繼續寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d294e8568c8e7f337ad328dd2fee75bbc15adc","tid":816413,"uid":36479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b15f89e7ec103e98aafe9281fbfee74956bce82","tid":816413,"uid":57308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6545f45df9595198c122f33a911b2f100c57d569","tid":816413,"uid":202767,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:00:46.000Z","msg":"希望大家鐘意，多廿個正皮繼續寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea6b8f82dbab83b29f8b3fde401a26b2caf0ce5","tid":816413,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"D &quot;{&quot; , &quot;}' 好7 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0a74afab4198367e97168de87f457329e6790a","tid":816413,"uid":136516,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"完啦好嘛 唔好再作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1884c984f5f056180f35d42600a8dd954a71